  "description": "<ul><li>🌟 We’re Hiring: Restaurant Supervisor 🌟</li></ul><p>📍 HarbourFront MRT (NE1 – Purple Line)</p><ul><li>🏢 Industry: Food Services (Chain Restaurant)</li></ul><p>💰 Salary & Benefits</p><ul><li>Basic Salary: SGD 4,000 – 4,500</li><li>Monthly Off Days: 6 days</li><li>Break Time: 2.5 hours daily</li><li>Meal Allowance</li><li>Annual Company Trip</li><li>Team-Building Activities</li><li>Annual & Sick Leave: In accordance with MOM regulations</li></ul><p>⸻ ⏰ Working Hours</p><ul><li>9:30 AM – 2:00 PM</li><li>4:30 PM – 10:00 PM</li></ul><p>(Comfortable split shift in a fully air-conditioned working environment)</p><p>⸻ 👨‍🍳 About the Role We are a well-established chain restaurant with a positive and supportive work culture, looking for an experienced Restaurant Supervisor to join our growing team. This role is ideal for a motivated individual with strong leadership skills who enjoys managing daily operations and ensuring excellent service standards.</p><p>⸻ 🔑 Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Lead daily restaurant operations to ensure efficient workflow and seamless service delivery</li><li>Coordinate and monitor service staff activities to maintain high customer satisfaction and operational standards</li><li>Coach and support team members to enhance performance and foster a collaborative work environment</li><li>Implement and enforce company policies and operational procedures to ensure compliance and consistency</li><li>Resolve operational challenges proactively to maintain smooth restaurant functioning and customer experience</li></ul><p>⸻ ✅ Required Competencies and Certifications</p><ul><li>Proven experience in a Restaurant Supervisor or management role, demonstrating leadership and operational management skills</li></ul><p>⸻</p><p><strong>Preferred Competencies and Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Strong motivation and positive work attitude to drive team engagement and productivity</li><li>Demonstrated responsibility, proactivity, and initiative in managing work arrangements and daily tasks</li><li>Effective leadership and teamwork skills to support and guide service staff</li></ul>",
